{"tid":757661,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"【本土出產】有無人想（奇幻水晶緣）remake?？","createTime":"2018-07-27T04:45:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T07:28:03.000Z","uid":173631,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bbe6234605ce586f3a851d917ab1c7d522e2f031","tid":757661,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T04:45:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">《永恒傳說：奇幻水晶緣》是一款由香港GAMEONE遊戲公司最新開發的新型態3D角色扮演遊</span></strong>戲，不論是故事劇情、畫面繪制、戰鬥系統還是3D技術都達到了較高的水準。《永恒傳說》融合了東西方特色，在西方中古世紀的背景下加入了神秘的東方場景和建築，以及帶有鮮明東方色彩的NPC人物。遊戲中迷宮的設計兼具2D與3D特色，所有的角色都是通過特殊的2D卡通畫面加上即時的3D人物來表現，帶有濃厚的迪斯尼卡通特色。怪物們不但可愛，而且造型還很特別。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/124504_247b28a85d05cc465dcbbbd58991d45f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F124504_247b28a85d05cc465dcbbbd58991d45f.jpg&h=4ae0e90a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"130f172cc9c0efd5b6675081a4df8d532dc2b294","tid":757661,"uid":124471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T05:43:46.000Z","msg":"gameone 不了"},{"pid":"859b81358d8c0e8f161d6adbd9b7d3ebe4fc400b","tid":757661,"uid":9887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T07:28:03.000Z","msg":"Gameone晨早唔係十幾廿年前嗰間gameone"}]}